  "name": "11) Damage Rolls (Both)",
  "_id": "CJOK9y9zaz3G50kC",
  "pages": [
    {
      "sort": 100000,
      "name": "Weapon Damage",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "nAnfT3prxUcWuPAC",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>On the Combat Tab for Characters or under the weapons section for NPCs you will see a \"Damage\" score. Hover over this and you'll see the red glow.</p><p>Simply click on the damage score and the relevant dice will roll and a chat message appears showing the weapon, damage formula and the dice score.</p><p>By holding <strong>ALT</strong> whilst clicking you will roll Critical Damage (i.e. +4D6).</p><p></p><p>Alternatively, depending on the outcome of the combat roll you will be presented with a \"roll damage\" button which will make the roll, automatically adjusting for critical successes.</p><p></p><p></p>"
      },
      "video": {
        "controls": true,
