    {
      "sort": 200000,
      "name": "Horse Damage",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "HW6JQrGlDvPURzrF",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>If you need to roll horse damage separately then go to the Companions tab, choose the relevant horse from the list and then click on the Damage to make the roll.</p><p>To choose Charge Damage hold <strong>SHIFT + click</strong> on the damage formula. The tooltip will show you the Charge Damage value.</p><p>By holding <strong>ALT + click</strong> you will roll Critical Damage (i.e. +4D6).</p><p>Holding <strong>ALT + SHIFT + click</strong> you will roll Critical Charge Damage.</p><p>The dice will roll and the result will be displayed as a chat message.</p><p></p><p>Changing the SHIFT game setting does not change this - keep holding SHIFT for charge damage.</p>"
      },
